To clean up the decorators in the story file, you can extract the logic within the decorator function into separate functions for better readability and maintainability. Here's an example of how you can refactor the decorator function:

1. Extract the logic for setting up Redux store, HTTP client, and other providers into separate functions:

```tsx
const setupReduxProvider = () => {
